metadata.title: XS Power XPFLEX4RD-100 XP/XS Flex Iced Red 100' Spool High Current Battery Cable
features: Easy to use in any installation
description: XP Flex Cable is a true AWG cable. The XP flex cable is also designed to be super flexible and easy to use in any installation. Has 10 percent oxygen free copper (OFC) and 90 percent copper clad aluminum (CCA). 2,009 strand count and soft touch PVC casing with 4 AWG cable.
